<p><a name="History" id="History"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Information_and_communication_technologies_for_development&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: History">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">History</span></h2>
<p>There have been numerous <a href="/wiki/Telecentre" title="Telecentre">telecentres</a> established in developing countries to improve acceess to ICTs. However, <a href="/wiki/Mobile_phone" title="Mobile phone">mobile phone</a> usage and <a href="/wiki/Mobile_telecommunications" title="Mobile telecommunications">mobile telecommunications</a> in general help to raise the ICT index of many developing countries.</p>
<p><a name="Projects" id="Projects"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Information_and_communication_technologies_for_development&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Projects">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Projects</span></h2>
<div class="thumb tright">
